text: Chanda Rigby (born April 16, 1968) is an American basketball coach. Since 2012, she has been the head coach of the Troy Trojans women's basketball team. ==Head coaching record== ===NJCAA=== ===NCAA=== ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:People from Franklinton, Louisiana Category:American women's basketball coaches
